{"tid":1154423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<高雄人大> 國民黨市議員要官員起立為韓國瑜鼓掌      洪慈庸：看到這畫面感到毛骨悚然","createTime":"2019-05-14T09:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T10:36:18.000Z","uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1815a67546526d49549dc84cdad7a0e5c02c94a","tid":1154423,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:45:18.000Z","msg":"議員要官員起立為韓國瑜鼓掌 洪慈庸：毛骨悚然<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕國民黨高雄市議員王義雄今（13日）上午質詢時，除稱讚市長韓國瑜6顆星與101分，還要求在場列席的官員起立鼓掌，讓部分官員感到尷尬、錯愕。<span style=\"color: red;\">有網友酸說，「這場景我在中國人大有看過」；時代力量立委洪慈庸也說，「看到這畫面感到毛骨悚然」。</span><br />\n<br />\n王義雄今質詢一開場就說給韓國瑜6顆星、101分，還形容韓有魄力、有毅力、有決心、有擔當、有格局、有國際觀，一心為市民生計打拚，是苦民所苦、民之所欲的市長；接著，王義雄還要求全場列席的高市府官員起立，「大家拍拍手，為市長的表現鼓勵」，此話一出全場傻眼，也有官員表情瞬間錯愕。<br />\n<br />\n「看到這畫面感到毛骨悚然，試想立法委員要求全體起立為行政院長鼓掌會是多荒謬的畫面？」洪慈庸在臉書直批，民代問政監督，政府做得好就期勉加強，做得不好就指正，有理有據，怠職生弊該罵就罵，該怎麼做就督促政府怎麼做，這是政府能進步的契機。「用誇張的馬屁去奉承一個首長意義何在？對社會進步有什麼好處呢？」<br />\n<br />\n洪慈庸也提到，替時力各地的議員們加油，新政治的改革，真的要繼續在地方深化。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2789912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2789912&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=c1adbbcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2789912</a>"},{"pid":"18b84dcd3df1ecb9d1f6850f6548ed30d05009eb","tid":1154423,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:45:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9PDuqxKxly8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9PDuqxKxly8&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=9c0dbbd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9PDuqxKxly8</a>"},{"pid":"4fd77b3f36452c613115ef751198c120b6fc75db","tid":1154423,"uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:50:29.000Z","msg":"高雄班人係咪ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳云根去台灣, 應該可以選到總統<br />\n<br />\n成個台灣, 真係放大版青山醫院黎"},{"pid":"3bb92d3d91a9067adf78e3ff1c0929f7c7a72657","tid":1154423,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i3.sinaimg.cn/dy/2013/0319/U7724P1DT20130319075253.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi3.sinaimg.cn%2Fdy%2F2013%2F0319%2FU7724P1DT20130319075253.jpg&h=5bde688f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19d08097fea16f8bc7dc8f1c5f827a465ea20d75","tid":1154423,"uid":30633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:12:51.000Z","msg":"拍手機器"},{"pid":"6393efd5db80d0433e6c30177ea5e0eabfd7d08f","tid":1154423,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"時代力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4569435be85f75ca72ec7f92cd42a8e0911005f","tid":1154423,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:36:18.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財有沒有人反對？<br />\n沒有<br />\n沒有<br />\n沒有<br />\n通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}